text: KKDS-LP (97.7 FM) is a radio station broadcasting to the Eureka, California area. It serves the Eureka area. The station is currently owned by Dell' Arte, Inc. ==See also== *List of community radio stations in the United States ==External links== * KDS-LP KDS-LP Category:Community radio stations in the United States Category:Mass media in Humboldt County, California
